{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0002", "text": "這 公開祕密若無人議異 我決心守一世", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 3, 4, 2, 2, 0, 0, 5, 2, 5, 4, 3, 9, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ze5", "gung1", "hoi1", "bei3", "mat6", "joek6", "mou4", "jan4", "ji5", "ji6", "ngo5", "kyut3", "sam1", "sau2", "jat1", "sai3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "公開", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "祕密", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "議異", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "決心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "守", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一世", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0003", "text": "你與我有什麼關連舉世亦已心照", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 5, 5, 2, 3, 3, 0, 9, 4, 2, 5, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "jyu5", "ngo5", "jau5", "sam6", "mo1", "gwaan1", "lin4", "geoi2", "sai3", "jik6", "ji5", "sam1", "ziu3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "與", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "關連", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "舉世", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心照", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0004", "text": "何必抱着上街招搖 在派對內炫耀", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 5, 2, 3, 3, 0, 2, 4, 4, 2, 2, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho4", "bit1", "pou5", "zoek6", "gaai1", "ziu1", "jiu4", "zoi6", "paai3", "deoi3", "noi6", "jyun6", "jiu6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "何必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抱", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上街", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "招搖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "派", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對內", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "炫耀", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0005", "text": "肥皂劇那般公告世上經已沒有需要", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 2, 5, 3, 3, 4, 4, 3, 5, 2, 5, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["fei4", "zou6", "kek6", "naa5", "bun1", "gung1", "gou3", "sai3", "ging1", "ji5", "mut6", "jau5", "seoi1", "jiu3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "肥皂劇", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那般", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "公告", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "世上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "經已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "需要", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0006", "text": "拖着你不行進教堂 仍然沒那樣少", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 2, 5, 3, 0, 4, 4, 0, 0, 0, 2, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["to1", "zoek6", "nei5", "bat1", "hang4", "zeon3", "gaau3", "tong4", "jing4", "jin4", "mut6", "naa5", "joeng6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "拖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "行進", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "教堂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍然", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "少", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0007", "text": "但旁人始終不會明 盟約是着重在心境", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 0, 9, 3, 3, 0, 0, 4, 2, 2, 2, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "pong4", "jan4", "ci2", "zung1", "bat1", "ming4", "mang4", "joek3", "si6", "zoek6", "zoi6", "sam1", "ging2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "旁人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "始終", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "明", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "盟約", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着重", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心境", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0008", "text": "早已認定是對方 亦不必一張紙定情", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 5, 2, 2, 2, 4, 3, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3, 9, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zou2", "ji5", "jing6", "ding6", "si6", "deoi3", "fong1", "jik6", "bat1", "bit1", "jat1", "zoeng1", "zi2", "ding6", "cing4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "早已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "認定", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對方", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一張", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "紙", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "定情", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0009", "text": "用悠長的初戀證明 能夠共渡各種困境", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 0, 3, 3, 9, 4, 0, 0, 4, 2, 2, 4, 9, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jung6", "jau4", "coeng4", "dik1", "co1", "lyun2", "zing3", "ming4", "nang4", "gau3", "gung6", "dou6", "gok3", "zung2", "kwan3", "ging2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "用", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "悠長", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "初戀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "證明", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "共渡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "各種", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "困境", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0010", "text": "若幸福的結局 顯得脫俗 無名份但更溫馨", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 3, 3, 4, 2, 9, 3, 4, 2, 0, 0, 2, 2, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["joek6", "hang6", "fuk1", "dik1", "git3", "guk6", "hin2", "dak1", "tyut3", "zuk6", "mou4", "ming4", "fan6", "daan6", "wan1", "hing1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幸福", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "結局", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "顯得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "脫俗", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無名", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "份", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "溫馨", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0011", "text": "百萬對發過誓愛侶 最尾各自引退無緣份同居", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 4, 4, 4, 2, 4, 5, 4, 5, 4, 2, 5, 4, 0, 0, 2, 0, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["baak3", "maan6", "deoi3", "faat3", "gwo3", "sai6", "oi3", "leoi5", "zeoi3", "mei5", "gok3", "zi6", "jan5", "teoi3", "mou4", "jyun4", "fan6", "tung4", "geoi1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "百萬", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛侶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最尾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "各自", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "引退", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無緣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "份", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "同居", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0012", "text": "地老天荒或會只得我們仍能愛下去", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 3, 3, 2, 9, 3, 5, 0, 0, 0, 4, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["dei6", "lou5", "tin1", "fong1", "waak6", "zi2", "dak1", "ngo5", "mun4", "jing4", "nang4", "oi3", "haa6", "heoi3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "地老天荒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "或會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我們", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "下去", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "未婚妻", "artists": ["張智霖"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2226", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pm66ZyW_MjIyNg_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
